            <title>台网友 AI 还原高雄碎尸案疑犯容貌，台媒：警方指相似度达九成</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/12/ai-resemble-taiwan-murderer/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ai-resemble-taiwan-murderer</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/12/ai-resemble-taiwan-murderer/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 06:28:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1291249</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p data-start="37" data-end="134">台湾高雄市一名 72 岁男子涉嫌连环杀害 3 名高龄妇女并分尸，案件震惊全国。目前其真实容貌尚未曝光。有网友根据疑犯邻居描述，运用 AI 技术生成模拟肖像，执法人员查看后表示相似度极高，据悉更接近九成。</p><p data-start="37" data-end="134"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291251" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/photo12-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/photo12-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/photo12-144x144.jpeg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/photo12.jpeg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-start="37" data-end="134">▲图片来源：<a href="https://udn.com/news/story/123018/8541078">udn</a></p><p data-start="136" data-end="227">据台媒报道，当地警方调查发现，疑犯涉及 3 宗命案，闭路电视画面亦显示有 3 个受害者进入疑犯住处后便人间蒸发，另外亦有闭路电视画面拍摄到疑匪疑似用单车运送尸块并弃置。尽管台湾执法人员已经掌握间接证据，疑犯至今拒不认罪，近日警察带疑犯重回案发现场重建案情，当时疑犯全身包裹严密，仅露出双眼，真实面貌仍旧成谜。有民众质疑为何要保护杀人犯。</p><p data-start="37" data-end="134"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291254" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250212001046-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250212001046-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250212001046.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-start="37" data-end="134">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20250212001041-260402?chdtv">中时新闻</a></p><p data-start="136" data-end="227">网友根据疑犯邻居描述，将疑犯外貌特征输入 AI 图片生成软件绘制出疑犯模拟肖像，特征包括平头、浓眉大眼及脸上有胡渣。《联合新闻》取得 AI 图片后曾向执法人员查询，执法专案人员查看后直言：「相似度极高。」、「有 9 成相似」。</p><p data-start="136" data-end="227">《联合新闻》引述台湾律师吴春生指，通缉犯通常会公开面貌与特征，但本案因疑犯尚未认罪，故暂未可以对外公布其真实容貌。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://udn.com/news/story/123018/8541078">联合新闻网</a>、<a href="https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E9%9B%84%E7%A2%8E%E5%B1%8D%E9%AD%94%E5%AE%B9%E8%B2%8C%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-ai%E9%82%84%E5%8E%9F-%E9%AD%94%E7%9B%B8-101410527.html">中天新闻</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
